'''Bastion Defense''' was the defense [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] that was assigned to protect [[Bastion/Legends|Bastion]] when the [[Emperor/Legends|emperor]]-in-exile [[Roan Fel]] made it his headquarters. The fleet consisted mainly of [[Pellaeon-class Star Destroyer|''Pellaeon''-class Star Destroyers]] and planetary [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolasers]] placed on the surface of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. Its headquarters was based in the [[Bastion Central Command Post]].<ref name="Legacy">[[Legacy (2006) 13]]</ref>

